replies.body:
Ah.... The removal of RGM's every patch. I didn't know I dreaded this until now. The alternate game modes were a real staple in my group of friends' weekends if there was one we all really enjoyed, like All-for-One and Poro King. 

Would it really be too much to ask to at least keep the good modes that people enjoy for longer periods? Invasion was an absolute blast that almost everybody loved. It'd be nice to keep certain modes for lengthily periods rather than for only 1 patch and then nothing for 3 patches while we wait for the next mode... 

{{sticker:sg-soraka}}
